  on { link_abs("http://www.facebook.com/lensflaregames", "Facebook") }.</p>

  <p>If you'd like to send us private feedback for one of our games
  (problems, praise, questions, anything), you can also send that to
  { link_abs("mailto:support@lensflare.com", "support@lensflare.com") }.
  </p>

</div>

